<!-- FAVORITE MOVIES / SERIES -->
<section>
<h2>My Top 3 Favourite Movies / Series</h2>

<article class="movie-card">
    <img src="images/images/lagenda budak setan.jpg" alt="Lagenda Budak Setan">

    <div class="movie-text">
        <h3>Lagenda Budak Setan</h3>

        <p>
            <span>Synopsis:</span><br>
            This movie tells the love story between Kasyah and Ayu, starting from their school days
            until adulthood. Their relationship is filled with challenges, misunderstandings,
            and emotional moments that test true love.
        </p>

        <p>
            <span>Why I Like It:</span><br>
            I like this movie because it shows realistic love struggles and deep emotions.
            The story feels close to real life and teaches patience, loyalty, and sincerity in relationships.
        </p>
    </div>
</article>

<article class="movie-card">
    <img src="images/images/one piece.jpg" alt="One Piece">

    <div class="movie-text">
        <h3>One Piece</h3>

        <p>
            <span>Synopsis:</span><br>
            One Piece follows Monkey D. Luffy and his pirate crew as they travel across the seas
            searching for the legendary treasure known as “One Piece” to become the Pirate King.
        </p>

        <p>
            <span>Why I Like It:</span><br>
            I like One Piece because of its strong themes of friendship, dreams, and never giving up.
            Each character has a meaningful backstory, making the series emotional and inspiring.
        </p>
    </div>
</article>

<article class="movie-card">
    <img src="images/images/money heist.jpg" alt="Money Heist">

    <div class="movie-text">
        <h3>Money Heist</h3>

        <p>
            <span>Synopsis:</span><br>
            Money Heist is about a criminal mastermind known as “The Professor” who plans the
            biggest heist in history by robbing the Royal Mint of Spain with a team of skilled criminals.
        </p>

        <p>
            <span>Why I Like It:</span><br>
            I like this series because it is intense, full of suspense, and unpredictable.
            The characters are smart and strategic, making every episode exciting to watch.
        </p>
    </div>
</article>

</section>

